  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dbd\u0dc1\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d9a\u0d82\u0da0\u0db1\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd3.\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2.\u0da9\u0dd3.\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dab\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A complaint to the CID from Balashakki Minister Kanchana",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Electricity and Power Minister Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera said today (18) afternoon that a complaint was made to the Criminal Investigation Department (CID) to investigate some of the main activities of the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation and the Ceylon Petroleum Stock Terminal.",
        "The Minister further said that he requested to investigate the activities related to procurement of fuel, evaluation of proposals, non-ordering, selection of suppliers and distribution irregularities."
      ],
